Online Shopping System

The system has 2 users. One being the customer and the other being the Admin.
There is basic details saved for both the users.
The customer can buy items, or view the cart or change the delivery address.
And the Admin can modify customer or ban customers, handle their issues or complains, manage a category of products or manage individual products as well.
Every customer has a shopping cart full of products where the can add, remove or clear it.
All the products are categorised.
he customer has the list of past or active orders where they can modify or cancel the order and choose a mode of payment.
